HEADWORD: Controvertist
<hw>Con"tro*ver`tist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One skilled
in or given to controversy; a controversialist.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>How unfriendly is the <qex>controvertist</qex> to the discernment
of the critic!</q> <rj><qau>Campbell.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

